Class NodeTypeCache

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.jackrabbit.jcr2spi.nodetype.NodeTypeCache

public class NodeTypeCache
extends Object

NodeTypeCache implements a cache for QNodeTypeDefinitions on a userId basis.
